memercayai Anda, Pak Presiden.

258
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,650
Pak Presiden.

259
00:17:09,192 --> 00:17:10,527
Buktikan pada mereka.

260
00:17:12,195 --> 00:17:14,239
