Ada alasan khusus perusahaan ini dipakai?

300
00:20:17,964 --> 00:20:20,299
Mungkin rekomendasi seseorang?

301
00:20:21,259 --> 00:20:22,844
Ada proses tender terbuka.

302
00:20:23,219 --> 00:20:25,596
Cuma ada satu alasan.

303
00:20:27,515 --> 00:20:28,558
Harga kompetitif.

304
00:20:32,145 --> 00:20:34,105
MANAJER KIM YONG-HUN

305
00:20:34,188 --> 00:20:36,816
Pertama, kita temukan
perusahaan instalasi kabel itu.

306
00:20:37,150 --> 00:20:39,110
Tolong sampaikan ke para atasan.

307
00:20:39,235 --> 00:20:42,405
Kontak kepolisian lokal
