01:03:13,078 --> 01:03:14,329
Ada masalah?

886
01:03:21,003 --> 01:03:22,963
Klienku Jin-ju...

887
01:03:27,175 --> 01:03:28,385
Dia meninggal

888
01:03:29,720 --> 01:03:30,762
barusan.

889
01:03:33,932 --> 01:03:36,643
Dia hanya perlu suntik hormon
agar bisa sembuh,

890
01:03:38,353 --> 01:03:40,397
